  "body": "This PR tracks to the progress to align Prysm to v.0.12.2 which is the target version for Medella testnet\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/releases/tag/v0.12.2\r\n\r\n## Beacon chain ‚õìÔ∏è \r\n\r\n- [x] Add DEPOSIT_CHAIN_ID and DEPOSIT_NETWORK_ID to configuration (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1988)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Compute committee count per slot is epoch based and rewrite gossip condition to be less stateful (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1904)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Apply strict uint64 casting (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1746, https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1935)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Separate config files by phases (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1882)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Reorder conditions to validator target_epoch before its use (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1996)\r\n\r\n##  Fork choice üç¥ \r\n\r\n- [x] [bug-fix] Fix edgecase in updating target checkpoint state (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1886)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Use parent_root in ancestor check to add mutations after assertions (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1884)\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Avoid redundant call to get_ancestor (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1880)\r\n\r\n##  Validator üßë‚Äçü§ù‚Äçüßë \r\n\r\n- [x] [non-substantive] Fix param in epoch_boundary_block_root calculation (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1962)\r\n\r\n##  Networking üñ•Ô∏è \r\n\r\n- [x] Add queuing possibility to p2p messages in gossip (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1956)\r\n- [x] Update gossipsub config params and add FAQ for explanation of choices (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1958)\r\n- [x] Remove ssz encoding from req/resp (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1982) #6415\r\n- [x] Add gossip conditions that block must have finalized checkpoint as ancestor (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1985) #6549 \r\n- [x] [non-substantive] p2p formatting RP (https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1953)\r\n\r\n## Spec test\r\n- [x] Update spec tests #6713 ",
